# Cloudflare Pages rewrites — production-only.
# In dev, Vite's proxy in vite.config.js forwards /api/* to the local FastAPI.
# In prod, the /api endpoints are pre-generated static JSON files.
# Status 200 = rewrite (URL stays the same), so the existing frontend code
# can keep calling /api/articles?... unchanged.

/api/articles*    /api/articles.json    200
/api/trends/kr*   /api/trends/kr.json   200

# SPA fallback — any unknown path returns the index so client-side routing works.
/*    /index.html    200
